title: Pixel 5 can't find Chromecast when trying to cast but does see it from the Google Home app.
content:
When trying to cast my phone or Youtube video it doesn't find Chromecast. However 
within Google Home I can access the Chromecast. I can change the ambient. I can play music. But only through Google Home. Casting doesn't see the Chromecast I have the 2nd generation Chromecast. I should mention other devices are able to cast to the Chromecast just not my Pixel 5.
